# kui-react — Windsurf rules
# Canonical source: AGENTS.md

## Discovery first

Before generating code, fetch the AI-facing catalog:

- `GET /api/registry?index=1` — every component, theme, design token, convention (no source, ~5x smaller)
- `GET /api/registry` — same plus full inline source per component + variants
- `GET /llms-full.txt` — markdown dump for paste-into-context
- Offline fallback: `public/registry/components.json`

Filter `components[]` by `layer` (ui | app | domain | theme), `category`, `name`, or `filePath`. Follow `composes[]` recursively to know what else to copy when porting a component; `usedBy[]` is the inverse.

## Hard rules

1. `'use client';` at top of every `modules/ui/`, `modules/app/`, `modules/domains/` file. Theme `layout.tsx` is client; theme `page.tsx` is server unless it owns state.
2. Named exports only. No default exports (excluding `next/dynamic` wrappers).
3. `cn()` from `@/libs/utils/cn` for classNames. Never template-literal or string-concat classes.
4. Token-only styling: `bg-primary`, `text-text-secondary`, `border-border-focus`. Never raw hex / rgb / hsl.
5. Icons: Font Awesome only. Named imports from `@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons` / `free-brands-svg-icons`. No `lucide-react`, `heroicons`, `react-icons`, inline SVG, or emoji as icons.
6. Accessibility on every interactive element:
   - `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-border-focus`
   - `aria-busy` / `aria-invalid` / `aria-describedby` / `aria-pressed` / `aria-expanded` per pattern
   - `disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed`
   - `aria-hidden="true"` on decorative `<FontAwesomeIcon>`
7. Spread `...rest` to the root element.
8. No business logic in `modules/ui/` — data fetching, routing, external calls belong in `modules/app/` or `modules/domains/`.

## Where new code goes

| Building | Location |
| --- | --- |
| Atom / molecule | `modules/ui/` |
| Organism / shell / form | `modules/app/` |
| Industry component | `modules/domains/<vertical>/` |
| New vertical | `modules/domains/<vertical>/` + `modules/showcase/data/sections/domain-<vertical>.showcase.tsx` + entry in `modules/showcase/data/showcase.menu.ts` |
| Full multi-page demo | `app/theme/<vertical>/` |

## Path aliases

`@/` → project root  ·  `@/modules/ui/...`  ·  `@/modules/app/...`  ·  `@/modules/domains/<vertical>`  ·  `@/libs/utils/cn`

## Template

```tsx
'use client';
import { cn } from '@/libs/utils/cn';

type Variant = 'primary' | 'secondary';
const variantClasses: Record<Variant, string> = {
  primary:   'bg-primary text-primary-fg hover:bg-primary-hover',
  secondary: 'bg-secondary text-secondary-fg hover:bg-secondary-hover',
};

type Props = { variant?: Variant; className?: string } & React.HTMLAttributes<HTMLDivElement>;

export function MyComponent({ variant = 'primary', className, children, ...rest }: Props) {
  return (
    <div
      className={cn(
        'rounded-md px-4 py-2 transition-colors',
        'focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-border-focus',
        variantClasses[variant],
        className,
      )}
      {...rest}
    >
      {children}
    </div>
  );
}
```
